## Chat-A3 Streaming Content Renderer Architecture
**Status:** approved
**Tags:** stack:frontend

| Component | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| `useStreamingDocument.ts` | Parses interleaved markdown + JSON blocks from SSE chunks |
| `StreamingRenderer.vue` | Receives segments array, renders markdown or registered components |
| `StreamingTable.vue` | Renders JSON table data with sticky headers |
| `SseParser` (backend) | Handles `\r\n\r\n` and `\n\n` delimiters robustly |

- Parser maintains a sticky props cache so partial JSON tables don't lose column definitions
- Component registry is extensible: add `{ table: StreamingTable }` to support new block types

